### ============================================================
### Mall Cloud — 管理后台全量接口文档（附请求/响应示例）
###
### 按 docs/36-前端接口清单.md 功能域 A-K 排列
### 用法：IDEA 打开 → 先跑 Step 0 获取 Token → 再跑后面的
### ============================================================

@ADMIN = http://localhost:8030
@BFF = http://localhost:8090
@BASIC = http://localhost:8022
@PRODUCT = http://localhost:8023
@MARKETING = http://localhost:8024
@ORDER = http://localhost:8026
@INVENTORY = http://localhost:8036
@MESSAGE = http://localhost:8028


### ============================================================
### Step 0：获取 Token
### ============================================================

# @name login
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/testLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"admin","password":"admin123"}

### 响应：
### {"code":200,"data":{"token":"eyJhbG...","user":{"id":13,"userName":"admin"}}}


### ============================================================
### 功能域 A：RBAC（认证与权限）
### ============================================================

### ---------- A1 认证 ----------

### A1.1 获取验证码（无需 Token）
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"uuid":"xxx","img":"base64图片"}}
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/getCode

### A1.2 登录
### 请求体: {username, password}
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"token":"...","user":{...}}}
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"admin","password":"admin123"}

### ---------- 以下接口需要 Authorization: Bearer Token ----------

### A1.3 当前用户信息
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/userInfo
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### A1.4 用户详情
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/userDetail
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### A1.5 菜单树（侧边栏导航用）
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":[{"id":1,"name":"系统管理","children":[...]}]}
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}


### ---------- A2 用户管理 ----------

### A2.1 用户分页
### 请求体: {entity: 筛选条件, page: {pageNum, pageSize}}
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"list":[...],"total":100,"pageNum":1}}
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"entity":{},"page":{"pageNum":1,"pageSize":10}}

### A2.2 用户编辑数据（聚合角色+部门，用于编辑页初始化）
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/1/edit-data
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### A2.3 新增用户
### 请求体: {userName, phone, email, password, deptId, jobId, status}
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/insert
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"userName":"test","phone":"13800000001","email":"t@t.com","password":"123456","deptId":1,"jobId":1,"status":1}

### A2.4 修改用户
### 请求体: {id, ...需要修改的字段}
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"id":1,"email":"new@t.com","status":1}

### A2.5 删除用户
### 请求体: {ids: [待删除的ID列表]}
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/deleteByIds
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"ids":[999]}


### ---------- A3 角色管理 ----------

### A3.1 角色分页
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/system/role/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{}

### A3.2 角色列表（下拉选择器用）
