### ============================================================
### 功能域 B：商品
### ============================================================

### B1 商品管理

### B1.1 商品分页
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"list":[{"id":18333...,"name":"...","price":...}],"total":50}}
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/product/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"entity":{},"page":{"pageNum":1,"pageSize":10}}

### B1.2 商品详情
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/product/detail?id=1833339862330556416
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### B1.3 商品编辑数据（聚合商品+库存）
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"product":{...},"inventory":{...}}}
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/product/1/edit-data
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### B1.4 新增商品
POST {{PRODUCT}}/admin/v1/product/insert
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"name":"测试商品","price":99.99,"status":1,"categoryId":1806965539515801603,"brandId":1806609234968473601,"unitId":1807039393319260160}

### B1.5 修改商品
POST {{PRODUCT}}/admin/v1/product/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"id":1833339862330556416,"price":88.88}

### B1.6 删除商品
POST {{PRODUCT}}/admin/v1/product/deleteByIds
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"ids":[999]}

