### 功能域 I：库存
### ============================================================

### I1 库存查询
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"productId":18333...,"available":990,"frozen":10,"saleCount":500}}
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/inventory/1833339862330556416
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### I2 批量库存查询
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/inventory/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

[1833339862330556416]

### I3 入库（采购/调拨）
### 请求体: {productId, quantity, batchNo, warehouse}
### 响应: {"code":200,"data":{"rows":1}}
POST {{INVENTORY}}/v1/inventory/inbound
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"productId":1833339862330556416,"quantity":500,"batchNo":"PO20260719-001","supplier":"富士康","purchasePrice":3999.00,"warehouse":"A区-01"}


